Package common.datatype.chatroom

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAddReceiverType
    Well known data type for adding receiver.
    ICRExceptionStatusType
    ICRExceptionStatusType is a sub interface of IFailureStatusType, defines a concrete failure status due to exception.
    ICRFailureStatusType
    Well known data type for sending failure status
    ICRInstallCmdType
    Well known data type for installing command in a chat room.
    ICRRejectionStatusType
    ICRRejectionStatusType is a sub interface of IFailureStatusType, it defines a concrete failure status due to rejection.
    IRemoveReceiverType
    Well known data type for removing receiver.
